      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    HMRC urges businesses to act now to avoid delays
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Everyone in the UK who trades with Europe or under the Northern Ireland Protocol will be affected by new customs and tax rules from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

